body:
Sorry for taking so long to respond. Holiday season was rather busy.

I was looking through the /usr/local/lib folder and I've compiled a list of all the protobuf related files below:

```
libprotobuf.a
libprotobuf.la
libprotobuf-lite.a
libprotobuf-lite.la
libprotobuf-lite.so
libprotobuf-lite.so.11
libprotobuf-lite.so.11.0.0
libprotobuf.so
libprotobuf.so.11
libprotobuf.so.11.0.0
```
Also, according to `protoc --version` I currently have `libprotoc 3.1.0` installed. Could this be causing the mismatch? Should I switch to a different version? As far as I know this is the most up to date version.
